org.hazelwire.modules
Class ModuleSelector

java.lang.Object
  org.hazelwire.modules.ModuleSelector

public class ModuleSelector
extends java.lang.Object

This class is responsible for managing everything that has to do with the set of modules in the backend. It will import, select, deselect both normal and hidden (system) modules.

Author:
Tim Strijdhorst
